  {
    "key": "KAN-1",
    "fields": {
      "summary": "Build Development Orchestrator agent (complexity gate)",
      "description": {
        "content": [
          {
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "Goal",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "type": "hardBreak"
              },
              {
                "text": "Read a Jira ticket, decide complex vs. easy, and dispatch the matching dev agent (Senior or Junior). Slot in the agentic workflow described in docs/agentic-workflow.md between the Ticket Agent and the dev agents.",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "type": "paragraph"
          },
          {
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "Open question to resolve in this ticket",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "type": "hardBreak"
              },
              {
                "text": "How is complex vs. easy decided? Options listed in docs/agentic-workflow.md: heuristic, classifier, or LLM judgment with calibration. Pick one and document the rationale in the README.",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "type": "paragraph"
          },
          {
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "Deliverables",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "type": "hardBreak"
              },
              {
                "text": "* agents/orchestrator/prompt.md - prompt following the structure of agents/jira-ticket/prompt.md (job, environment, scope, allowed mutations, forbidden, judgment rubric, stop criteria).",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "type": "hardBreak"
              },
              {
                "text": "* agents/orchestrator/README.md - README following the structure of agents/jira-ticket/README.md.",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "type": "hardBreak"
              },
              {
                "text": "* .github/workflows/orchestrator.yml - workflow modeled on .github/workflows/jira-ticket.yml. Reuse the install-jira-cli step, the write-config step from repo vars, the prompt heredoc, the anthropics/claude-code-action@v1 step, and the log-commit-to-main step (.github/workflows/jira-ticket.yml:97-114).",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "type": "paragraph"
          },
          {
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "Triggers",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "type": "hardBreak"
              },
              {
                "text": "* workflow_dispatch",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "type": "hardBreak"
              },
              {
                "text": "* schedule: cron staggered AFTER the ticket-agent run (17 7 * * * is taken, pick later e.g. 47 7 * * *).",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "type": "paragraph"
          },
          {
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "Allowed tools",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "type": "hardBreak"
              },
              {
                "text": "* Bash(jira:",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "marks": [
                  {
                    "type": "em"
                  }
                ],
                "text": ") and Bash(bin/jira:",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "text": ") for reading tickets.",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "type": "hardBreak"
              },
              {
                "text": "* Bash(gh workflow run:*) OR repository_dispatch payloads for invoking the dev workflows. Decide which and document.",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "type": "paragraph"
          },
          {
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "Acceptance criteria",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "type": "hardBreak"
              },
              {
                "text": "* A ticket judged complex dispatches senior-dev.yml; a ticket judged easy dispatches junior-dev.yml. Verified by running both a complex and an easy KAN ticket through the workflow manually.",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "type": "hardBreak"
              },
              {
                "text": "* Run log committed to .github/agent-logs/orchestrator/DATE/RUN_ID.json and visible in tools/viewer.sh.",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "type": "paragraph"
          }
        ],
